e a large swim platform allows all AQUA passengers to enjoy the optimal experience of accessing the water at sea level.” <img class="size-full wp-image-372612 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5.png" alt="" width="1307" height="883" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5.png 1307w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5-300x203.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5-1024x692.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5-768x519.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-5-1200x811.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-372614 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6.png" alt="" width="1300" height="886" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6.png 1300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6-300x204.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6-1024x698.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6-768x523.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-6-1200x818.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-372616 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7.png" alt="" width="1314" height="888" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7.png 1314w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7-300x203.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7-1024x692.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7-768x519.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-7-1200x811.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-372618 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8.png" alt="" width="1285" height="892" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8.png 1285w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8-300x208.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8-1024x711.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8-768x533.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Yacht-8-1200x833.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> Gates (64) has a net worth of $113.7 billion, according to the Bloomberg Billionaires Index, a ranking of the world’s 500 richest people. In 2010, he and Melinda Gates announced the Giving Pledge with Warren Buffett and asked other billionaires to sign to give away portions of their fortunes. As of May, 204 people from 23 countries have agreed to participate. Sinot has denied any links with the sale of the Aqua to Bill Gates and said that the design remains a concept. Read: How much money you need to earn to be in the top 1% in South Africa 